ED_Title: Report of the International Tribunal for the Prosecution of Persons Responsible for Serious Violations of International Humanitarian Law Committed in the Territory of the Former Yugoslavia since 1991
ED_DecisionText:
At its 44th plenary meeting, on 9 November 2016, the General Assembly took note of the twenty-third annual report of the International Tribunal for the Prosecution of Persons Responsible for Serious Violations of International Humanitarian Law Committed in the Territory of the Former Yugoslavia since 1991. 

(See A/71/263, A/71/PV.44)
ED_Disclaimer: The text of this decision is available in all languages in document A/71/49 (Vol. II).
